112 Then I will accuse Sapphira with her husband;
113 I will praise the kicks that Elyodorus had;
114 and in infamy all the mountain goes around

115 Polynestor who killed Polydorus;
116 lastly one shouts to us: “Crassus,
117 tell us, since you know: what is the taste of gold?”.
